{"bangumi":{"date":"2018-01-02","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/16/de/218708_99YjL.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/16/de/218708_99YjL.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/16/de/218708_99YjL.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/16/de/218708_99YjL.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/16/de/218708_99YjL.jpg"},"summary":"无论何时，我们的第一步总是从好奇心开始。\r\n不曾看过的风景，不曾听过的声音，不曾闻过的味道，不曾摸过的质感，不曾尝过的食物，以及不曾感受过的澎湃。\r\n为了重拾不知何时忘却的记忆碎片和不知何时舍弃的感动的旅途。\r\n在到达终点的时候，我们会想些什么呢？\r\n40度的咆哮，50度的疯狂，60度的呐喊，跨越荒芜的海源到达原生地域。\r\n在地球的天边，远离文明的南方尽头。\r\n这是向南极（比宇宙更远的地方）进发的四位女孩子的旅行物语。我们通过她们回想起生于明日的光辉！","name":"宇宙よりも遠い場所","name_cn":"比宇宙更远的地方","tags":[{"name":"原创","count":4043,"total_cont":0},{"name":"MADHouse","count":3380,"total_cont":0},{"name":"青春","count":3256,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2018年1月","count":2182,"total_cont":0},{"name":"花田十辉","count":1918,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":1850,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":1547,"total_cont":0},{"name":"南极","count":1530,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2018","count":1103,"total_cont":0},{"name":"百合","count":1084,"total_cont":0},{"name":"励志","count":926,"total_cont":0},{"name":"花泽香菜","count":818,"total_cont":0},{"name":"水濑祈","count":613,"total_cont":0},{"name":"早见沙织","count":549,"total_cont":0},{"name":"井口裕香","count":295,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":188,"total_cont":0},{"name":"石塚敦子","count":133,"total_cont":0},{"name":"花田十輝","count":115,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":102,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻百合","count":72,"total_cont":0},{"name":"旅行","count":66,"total_cont":0},{"name":"催泪","count":66,"total_cont":0},{"name":"友情","count":57,"total_cont":0},{"name":"いしづかあつこ","count":48,"total_cont":0},{"name":"冒险","count":46,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神作","count":42,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2018年","count":37,"total_cont":0},{"name":"石冢敦子","count":37,"total_cont":0},{"name":"比宇宙更远的地方","count":31,"total_cont":0},{"name":"校园","count":23,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key"